00:40:03.563 --> 00:40:05.563 line:85% position:50% size:80%
ODGŁOS DZWONKA PRZY DRZWIACH

00:40:20.199 --> 00:40:21.480 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No co, Milu?

00:40:22.039 --> 00:40:24.559 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
