01:31:38.039 --> 01:31:39.359 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Tak, tak.

01:31:40.439 --> 01:31:41.479 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Pewnie.

01:31:41.680 --> 01:31:43.319 line:85% position:50% size:80%
