01:33:46.800 --> 01:33:48.079 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Tak, śliczny.

01:34:13.359 --> 01:34:14.880 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Byłem w kościele.

01:34:16.640 --> 01:34:18.359 line:85% position:50% size:80%
